            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sophie, excuse me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Ah, Fritz, welcome. Do you need something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I have something to tell you today."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "What could it be...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I'd like to accompany you when you go gathering."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Huh? When I go gathering? That would really help me... But why all of a sudden?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Alchemists need to go to dangerous places to gather materials, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Oh, yes... Sometimes we fight scary monsters, so it's actually really hard work..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Indeed. I told you before that I was once a mercenary."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I'm confident in my skills due to my experience. I doubt any monster would have the upper hand over me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "You've been helping me quite a bit. I'd like to return the favor, if possible."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I see... Thank you very much. It would really help if you came along too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, just let me know when you're going gathering. I'll lend you my strength anytime."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I understand. I will!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "\"<CLGR>Fritz<CLNR>\" joined your party."
        }
